{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/btoa","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/btoa\"><code>Btoa</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<p>Tworzy string ASCII zakodowany w base-64 z ciągu (\"string\") danych binarnych.</p>\n<p>Metoda ta jednak nie nadaje się do konwertowania surowych ciągów <a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/standard/WhatIsUnicode.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Unicode</a>! Zobacz sekcję Unicode poniżej.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var zakodowaneDane = window.btoa(<em>ciagDoZakodowania</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> zakodowaneDane <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">btoa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// kodowanie ciągu</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> odkodowaneDane <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">atob</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>zakodowaneDane<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// odkodowywanie ciągu (\"Hello, world\")</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Uwagi","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Możesz używać tej metody do kodowania danych, które w innym wypadku mogą powodować problemy z komunikacją. Przekaż je, a następnie użyj metody <code><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/atob\" title=\"DOM/window.atob\">window.atob()</a></code> aby odkodować dane ponownie. Na przykład możesz zakodować znaki kontrolne takie jak ASCII o wartości od 0 do 31.</p>\n<p><code>btoa()</code> jest także dostępne dla komponentów XPCOM zaimplementowanych w JavaScript, nawet jeżeli <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window\" title=\"DOM/window\"><code>window</code></a> nie jest globalnym obiektem w komponencie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ciągi_unicode","title":"Ciągi Unicode","isH3":false,"content":"<p>W większości przeglądarek odwołanie się do <code>window.btoa()</code> z ciągiem Unicode spowoduje wystąpienie wyjątku <code>Character Out Of Range</code>.</p>\n<p>Aby tego uniknąć, rozważ ten model odnotowany przez <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://ecmanaut.blogspot.com/2006/07/encoding-decoding-utf8-in-javascript.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Johana Sundströma</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">str</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">btoa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> str <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">str</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">unescape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">decodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">atob</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> str <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Usage:</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'✓ à la mode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// JTI1dTI3MTMlMjUyMCUyNUUwJTI1MjBsYSUyNTIwbW9kZQ==</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'JTI1dTI3MTMlMjUyMCUyNUUwJTI1MjBsYSUyNTIwbW9kZQ=='</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"✓ à la mode\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'I \\u2661 Unicode!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// SSUyNTIwJTI1dTI2NjElMjUyMFVuaWNvZGUlMjUyMQ==</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'SSUyNTIwJTI1dTI2NjElMjUyMFVuaWNvZGUlMjUyMQ=='</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"I ♡ Unicode!\"</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Lepszym, bardziej wiarygodnym i mniej wymagającym rozwiązaniem jest konwersja <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">DOMString (en-US)</a></code> do ciągu zakodowanego w UTF-8 używając <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">TypedArray (en-US)</a>. W tym celu proszę zapoznać się z <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#solution_.232_.e2.80.93_rewriting_atob()_and_btoa()_using_typedarrays_and_utf-8\">tym akapitem</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Brak zmian od ostatniej migawki, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML 5.1' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Migawka <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. Bez zmian.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Migawka <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. Utworzenie <code>WindowBase64</code> (properties where on the target before it).</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility_2","title":"Zgodność przeglądarek","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n <div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Pulpit</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Funkcja</th>\n    <th>Chrome</th>\n    <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n    <th>Opera</th>\n    <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Podstawowa obsługa</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)[1]</td>\n    <td>10</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Funkcja</th>\n    <th>Android</th>\n    <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>IE Mobile</th>\n    <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n    <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Podstawowa obsługa</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n    <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<p>[1] <code>btoa()</code> jest także dostępna dla komponentów XPCOM zaimplementowanych w JavaScript, nawet jeżeli <code><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window\" lang=\"pl\">window</a></code> nie jest globalnym obiektem w komponencie<code>.</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Zobacz też","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/docs/Web/API/WindowBase64/Base64_encoding_and_decoding\">Kodowanie i dekodowanie Base64</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/Data_URLs\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">data URIs (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/atob\"><code>window.atob()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Przykład","id":"example"},{"text":"Uwagi","id":"notes"},{"text":"Ciągi Unicode","id":"ciągi_unicode"},{"text":"Specyfikacje","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Zgodność przeglądarek","id":"browser_compatibility_2"},{"text":"Zobacz też","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Tworzy string ASCII zakodowany w base-64 z ciągu (\"string\") danych binarnych.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cadenas binarias","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope.btoa()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/btoa","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/btoa/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/btoa","title":"WindowBase64.btoa()"}],"pageTitle":"WindowBase64.btoa() - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}